# Base packages file

This file contains a list of all the base packages that will be present in all installs.

## Utility

- 7zip

## Needed

- base-devel
- efibootmgr
- grub
- git
- man-db
- man-pages
- nano
- vi
- networkmanager SYSTEMD_ENABLE=NetworkManager
- os-prober
// needed for os-prober to work properly, but not in dependencies (what??)
- fuse3
- pacman-contrib
- sudo
- wget
- openssh

## Bluetooth

- bluez SYSTEMD_ENABLE=bluetooth
- bluez-utils

## Sound

- pipewire SYSTEMD_USER_ENABLE
- pipewire-pulse
- alsa-utils
- wireplumber

## Apps

- kitty
- feh
- blueman
- pavucontrol

### File manager

- yazi

## Desktop

- hyprland
- hyprlock
- hyprshot
- swww
- quickshell
- xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland
- sddm SYSTEMD_ENABLE

## Fonts

- noto-fonts-cjk
- noto-fonts-emoji
- ttf-ubuntu-mono-nerd

## File systems

- btrfs-progs
